|Example.Gloss=if well is certain that refl live times political is of hope that the messages of-the President derive in actions much more effective than the pretension of cure the cancer of the poverty in the country with more paltry handouts whose objective seems more the justify an expense administrative than impact in the nutrition of the impoverished
|Example.English translation=Since it's true that these are political times, we can only hope that the messages of the President lead to much more effective action than pretending to cure the cancer of poverty in the country with more paltry handouts, whose objective seems more to justify administrative costs than to have any effect on the nutrition of the malnourished.
